长期担任《我弥留之际》吉他手是最新一位因“困难和严重的情况”退出乐队的成员https://www.nme.com/news/music/longtime-as-i-lay-dying-guitarist-is-the-latest-member-to-quit-the-band-amid-difficult-and-serious-情况-3808518?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=长期的我垂死的吉他手是在困难和严重的情况下退出乐队的最新成员Surej SinghFri, 01 Nov 2024 02:46:46 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3808518 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>主唱蒂姆·兰贝西斯现在是乐队中仅存的成员</p><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/longtime-as-i-lay-dying-guitarist-is-the-latest-member-to-quit-the-band-amid-difficult-and-serious-situation-3808518">《Longtime As I Lay Dying》吉他手是最新一位因“困难而严重的情况”而退出乐队的成员，</a>这首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/as-i-lay-dying@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/as-i-lay-dying">《As I Lay Dying》的</a>长期吉他手 Phil Sgrosso 与他的几位乐队成员一起退出了乐队 - 请参阅下面 Sgrosso 对于他的离开有何评论。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/heriot-the-cover-interview-devoured-by-the-mouth-of-hell-3798080">赫瑞特已准备好掀起地狱</a></strong></li></ul><p>Sgrosso 于 2003 年加入乐队，他在社交媒体上宣布退出金属核乐队。 Sgrosso 退出之前，贝斯手 Ryan Neff、吉他手 Ken Susi 和鼓手 Nick Pierce（他们均于 2022 年加入 As I Lay Dying） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/three-members-quit-controversial-as-i-lay-dying-citing-personal-morals-3806056">宣布上个月（10 月 24 日）以“个人道德”为由退出</a>。</p><p>随着斯格罗索的退出，这支备受争议的乐队中唯一剩下的成员是主唱蒂姆·兰贝西斯。斯格罗索通过 Instagram 发帖谈到了他的离职，强调了“困难而严重的情况”。</p><p>斯格罗索写道：“最近发生的事件，包括乐队成员的离开以及新专辑发行前欧洲巡演的取消，很明显我们正处于困难和严重的境地。” </p><figure id="attachment_3808521" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3808521" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3808521" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/phil-sgrosso@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/phil-sgrosso@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/phil-sgrosso@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/phil-sgrosso@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/phil-sgrosso@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/phil-sgrosso@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/phil-sgrosso@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3808521" class="wp-caption-text">前《As I Lay Dying》吉他手 Phil Sgrosso。图片来源：Gary Wolstenholme/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p> “简而言之，最近的行动表明，《当我弥留之际》不再为任何参与者提供一个健康或安全的环境——无论是创造性的、个人的还是专业的。在目睹了一些令人担忧的行为模式后，我意识到，凭良心来说，我不能再采取可能对这个领域的任何工作人员产生负面影响的进一步行动。”</p><p>他继续说道：“出于这些原因，我觉得无论是在创作上还是在个人方面，与《弥留之际》完全保持距离对我来说是最有利的。我还想向瑞恩、肯和尼克表达我的全力支持，他们最近选择了离开。我很感谢我们过去三年的成就和友谊。”</p><p>在声明的最后，斯格罗索补充道：“当我弥留之际，功能失调一直阻碍着我，我觉得我不再有责任承担这个负担。”</p><p>请参阅下面吉他手的完整帖子。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBw5wSvya80/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.1